Usage: report_net_parasitics [-help] <net_name> [-file_name <string>]
                             -rc_corner <string>

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<net_name>              # Specifies the name of the net for which the RC
                        # parasitics are to be reported (string, required)
-file_name <string>     # Specifies the name of the output file
                        # (string, optional)
-rc_corner <string>     # Specifies the RC corner name for which the RC
                        # parasitics are to be reported (string, required)